{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "Now run the 30-second trace. **Place the SmartTag within 30–50 cm of the board and optionally press its button to trigger advertising:**", "ts": "2026-05-17T21:00:00+00:00", "time": "00:00:00"}
